      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOUBLEFAULT (4) is a colt by leading sire Art Major on debut for the Chantal Turpin yard. Has shown ability when second to a handy one in his two trials here. Could kick off with a win. HES A DANCER (3) is a colt by A Rocknroll Dance on debut. Has joined Jason Grimson since showing talent in his trials in country NSW. Anticipating a bright start to his career. FIT AND READY (2) draws well and is a likely improver after racing parked when debuting with a second to a runaway winner at this circuit and distance. LUCY RHAYNE BOW (7) is at the track for the first time. By Soho Tribeca and is another from the Turpin stable. Interesting to see what unfolds from this wide draw but was close-up in her latest trial so keep safe.",
